{"id": "art-61", "label": "Art. 61", "title": "Art. 61", "slug": "art-61", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 61 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_124870727\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2435\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_124870727\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Creditorii sociali <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\norice alte persoane prejudiciate prin hot&#259;rârile <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span>\nprivitoare la modificarea actului constitutiv pot formula o cerere de <span\nclass=SpellE>opozi&#355;ie</span> prin care s&#259; solicite <span\nclass=SpellE>instan&#355;ei</span> <span class=SpellE>judec&#259;tore&#351;ti</span>\ns&#259; oblige, dup&#259; caz, societatea sau <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span>\nla repararea prejudiciului cauzat.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)În sensul prezentei <i\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legi</i>, prin hot&#259;rârea <span\nclass=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span> se <span class=SpellE>în&#355;elege</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> hot&#259;rârea organelor statutare ale <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, iar termenul <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;i</span>\ninclude <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarii</span>,\nîn afar&#259; de cazul în care din context rezult&#259; altfel.</span></p>"}